{"tid":453851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★三色貓？英國貓殺手再出現　虐殺肢解逾370家貓","createTime":"2017-10-31T14:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T05:15:43.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1556525aa128424049fdabf899a5c1a4b1434251","tid":453851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:40:47.000Z","msg":"英國南部上周一（25日）至周日（29日）期間，發生了至少6宗貓隻虐殺案，警方懷疑惡名昭彰的「克羅伊登貓殺手」（Croydon Cat Killer）再度出現，相信這個貓殺手自2014年起，已殺死及肢解逾370隻貓。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，最初的「受害者」是赫特福德郡小鎮米蘭捷克（Potters Bar）的家貓泰滋（Taz），牠在失蹤一周後，其遺體於上周一被發現，身上有多處傷口。海斯、克羅伯勒、凱特福德等地亦相繼有另外5隻貓被虐殺，1隻名為羅斯迪（Rusty）的家貓，更在慘遭分屍被放到其主人門口。當局認為，有關的作案手法與過去的克羅伊登貓殺手如出一轍，故相信是由該名殺手犯下的案件。<br />\n<br />\n據報道，克羅伊登貓殺手自2014年起不斷殺害、肢解家貓及小動物，但警方目前仍未有拘捕疑犯，由於犯人最初作案的地區圍繞在M25高速公路，故亦有人稱其為「M25貓殺手」（M25 cat killer）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/photo/bknint-20171031160014487-1031_17011_001_01b.jpg?20171031180911\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20171031160014487-1031_17011_001_01b.jpg%3F20171031180911&h=5b8d6ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n泰滋（圖）是近日首先遭殺害的家貓。（互聯網圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bknint-20171031160014487-1031_17011_001.html?editorpickDate=20171031&amp;editorpickUuid=402882b15990b2a90159a58b79187810&amp;eventid=402882b15aad00a2015aae03e731261b&amp;eventsection=hk_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171031%2Fbknint-20171031160014487-1031_17011_001.html%3FeditorpickDate%3D20171031%26editorpickUuid%3D402882b15990b2a90159a58b79187810%26eventid%3D402882b15aad00a2015aae03e731261b%26eventsection%3Dhk_news&d=183tMSu8fj4vslgrYfXG%2Bf7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=7b9d0272\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20171031/bknint-20171031160014487-1031_17011_001.html?editorpickDate=20171031&amp;editorpickUuid=402882b15990b2a90159a58b79187810&amp;eventid=402882b15aad00a2015aae03e731261b&amp;eventsection=hk_news</a>"},{"pid":"676ab01e5cce5045c9c90c74ee6e951ef4309e9d","tid":453851,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de99662562c5c2eb5d1303886628d6aa896ed543","tid":453851,"uid":22858,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:42:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>悼念三色貓</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada2a48873fbca836eed93bd0d9e755fec06b059","tid":453851,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:42:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>悼念三色貓</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53bf50fe7746d3a3cc03d6a0316321bfffc9285b","tid":453851,"uid":132326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d04aae161616d14bec1673505db21d208838d2","tid":453851,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T14:44:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>悼念三色貓</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\